This directory contains the code for running different bottle collecting 
programs.

---------------------------------------

bottleCollector.qlg - a single bottle collector

coopBottleCollector.qlg - two bottle collector cooperating to avoid collisions
and keeping track of the total number of bottles collected

tasksBottleCollector.qlg - two bottle collector robots controlled by a single
agent running a task for each robot.

---------------------------------------

When running the programs you are able to interact with the environment so as
to observe how the agents react to changes.

Clicking on a bottle with Button-1 and then dragging will move the selected
bottle.

Control-Button-1 or Button-2 will add a bottle at the selected spot

Control-Shift-Button-1 or Button-3 when clicked on a bottle will remove
  that bottle

Pressing the Space bar will toggle running the simulator.